Text:
Ill'ing !! I'm loving Providance... Gonna spread the word C!nCh!lla - fresher than breast milk. 

Thanks guys :)

Good stuff guys. I just woke up and your sound is sitting very well with me atm. The distortion sample (I thought of it as anyway) on better days, helped counteract the fuzz in my head perfectly. I'm now onto the next EP and loving the electro/rock combo, very smoothly done guys, keep doing what you are for a while. Hope you fancy a trip down to Melbourne in the not to distant future too :)
Oh and thanks for making the EPs free via TPB, I probably wouldn't have heard you otherwise. I'll donate via your website soon. Cheers

Wouldn't have heard of you guys were it not for TPB, but definitely glad I did.
Dig this stuff like a gardener, keep up the good work.  Will spread the good word!
Thx much, keep rubbin the funk on strong!
